        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You reduce a creature to 0 Hit Points.</p><hr /><p>You effortlessly enter a state of flow in combat. When you use Battle Focus and each time you reduce a hostile creature to 0 Hit Points in the next minute, you regain @Damage[@actor.level[healing]] Hit Points equal to your level. If you're @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Wounded], you can reduce the wounded condition by 1 instead of regaining Hit Points.</p>"
